/www.nme.com/reviews/taylor-swift-reputation-album-review-2158267-2158267">声誉</a>”开始进入“最终游戏”，然后是Sheeran自己的歌“大声思考”。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/taylor-swift-live-in-edinburgh-3763814?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTEAAR3aUrwDuJgnDfhL31UDsmnsruamExATeZ01eTeIL676mvOLqfs_qSqlcDA_aem_AdsNpowi-Oeil7ifBwJkCYIrutAyvrSApL7euoOaAMY46dLmNBFUoLD_G-AIDSNpm0UoyBr960w58VftuHOrt-ne">在爱丁堡举行的英国“Eras Tour”揭幕战</a>的五星级评论中写道：“尽管这是一场舞台表演，但在一个巨大、洞穴般的场地中，斯威夫特和她的歌迷们成功地建立了一个社区。</p><p> “陌生人交换友谊手镯，一起欢笑，一起哭泣，拥抱巡演中的笑话和传说（例如在‘精致’期间大喊‘一、二、三，让我们去吧’）。这就是斯威夫特的力量，这位艺术家<a href="https://news.stv.tv/north/loch-tay-renamed-in-honour-of-taylor-swift-ahead-of-sold-out-murrayfield-concerts-in-edinburgh">不仅激发了苏格兰湖的重新命名</a>，还激发了无数粉丝站出来拥抱成为 Eras 家族的一员。 </p><figure id="attachment_3785023" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3785023" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785023" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 于 2024 年 8 月 15 日在英国伦敦温布利体育场举行的“泰勒·斯威夫特 | The Eras 巡演”中登台表演。 （Gareth Cattermole/TAS24的照片/TAS权利管理的Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Taylor-Swift-performing-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785023" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在“泰勒·斯威夫特 | “The Eras Tour”将于 2024 年 8 月 15 日在英国伦敦温布利球场举行。 （Gareth Cattermole/TAS24的照片/TAS权利管理的Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><div id="playlist-player-jwplayer"><div class="playlist-player-container"><p> 继本月的伦敦演出后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-new-2024-north-american-eras-dates-3478541">斯威夫特将于今年秋天返回北美</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-confirms-the-eras-tour-will-end-in-december-3765542">于 12 月初在加拿大温哥华结束她庞大的“Eras 巡演”</a> 。</p><p>斯威夫特在利物浦举行第 100 场“Eras Tour”演出时对观众说：“这次巡演绝对是我一生中最累、最全面、最快乐、最有价值、最美妙的事情。”六月。</p><p>这些节目标志着自从上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-cancels-vienna-eras-shows-following-planned-terror-plot-3781881">在维也纳取消了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyer-for-suspect-in-taylor-swift-vienna-terror-plot-says-accusations-are-exaggerated-3783655">挫败恐怖袭击情节，</a>斯威夫特的三场演出被取消了，这是第一次“时代”音乐会。</p><p>事件发生后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-changes-wembley-stage-times-following-foiled-vienna-terror-plot-3783073">，斯威夫特最近在伦敦的舞台时间不得不进行调整</a>。温布利大球场还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tay-gating-wembley-stadium-issues-statement-to-taylor-swift-fans-hoping-to-gather-outside-venue-3783014">发表声明，警告无票球迷在音乐会举行期间不能站在场外</a>，这种趋势被称为“泰式门控”。</p><p>代表所谓的维也纳音乐会恐怖情节中代表主要嫌疑人的律师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyer-for-suspect-in-taylor-swift-vienna-terror-plot-says-accusations-are-exaggerated-3783655">声称，针对其客户的指控被夸大了</a>。</p><p>据称与主要嫌疑人接触后，上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-teenager-arrested-over-taylor-swift-show-terror-plot-in-vienna-3782385">被警方逮捕了第三名嫌疑人</a>。斯威夫特尚未对这一事件发表评论。</p></div></div><p>邮报<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-florence-welch-and-jack-antonoff-join-taylor-swift-on-stage-at-wembley-stadium-3785394">观看佛罗伦萨·韦尔奇（Florence Welch）和杰克·安东诺夫（Jack Antonoff）加入泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）在温布利体育场（Wembley Stadium）的舞台上</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Ulver 键盘手 Tore Ylwizaker 去世，享年 54 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/tore-ylwizaker-ulvor-keyboardist-dies-dies-age--54-3785379?utm_source=rsss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = tore = tore = tore-campaign=tore-ylylwizaker-ulver-ulver-ulver-keykeyboardisist-54Laura Molloy Tue, 20 Aug 2024 21:08:08 +0000 Music NewsNews..ElectronicRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3785379 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ulver的Tore Ylwizaker于2011年11月5日在利兹大学在英国利兹大学举行的舞台上演出。学分：Gary Wolstenholme/Redferns" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>没有死亡原因</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tore-ylwizaker-ulver-keyboardist-dies-aged-54-3785379">撕裂Ylwizaker，Ulver键盘手去世，享年54岁，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Ulver的Tore Ylwizaker于2011年11月5日在利兹大学在英国利兹大学举行的舞台上演出。学分：Gary Wolstenholme/Redferns" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Tore-Ylwizaker-of-Ulver-performs-on-stage-during-Damnation-Festival-at-Leeds-University-on-November-5-2011-in-Leeds-United-Kingdom.-Credit_-Gary-Wolstenholme_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>挪威电子经验性集体ULVER的键盘手Tore Ylwizaker享年54岁。没有给出死亡原因。</p><p>他的乐队成员昨天（8月19日）宣布了他在社交媒体帖子中的去世。</p><p>他们写道：“正是在我们心中的黑洞中，我们必须告诉你，近三十多年来，我们的兄弟撕毁了Ylvisaker（Ylwizaker），”他们写道。 “他在54岁生日的8月16日晚上去世。”</p><p>声明接着说：“目前这一切都难以接受。我们一收拾好就回来。安息吧，最亲爱的朋友。我们爱你，永远。”</p><p> Ylwizaker 于 1997 年应主唱兼创始人 Kristoffer Rygg 的邀请加入 Ulver。他被招募来拓展乐队的艺术视野，他对乐队 1998 年专辑《威廉·布莱克的天堂与地狱的婚姻主题》的贡献随后见证了 Ulver 从民谣和黑金属起源过渡到后来出现的前卫音乐。定义它们。</p><p> Ylwizaker还为Ulver制作了他的角色，尤其是在2002年的“ Ash的Star of Ash&#39;s Iter.Viator”上工作。以及2008年的“你什么时候保持沉默”。他还为诸如ihsahn，Mayhem，Ash和Arcturus之星等乐队制作，录制和混合。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-2gg4uKB3Y/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org